<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.287339>
    dc:description "FIGURES 7 – 10. Dorsal photographs of heads and pronota. 7. U. assamensis; 8. U. jingae sp. nov.; 9. U. angusta sp. nov.; 10. U. magna sp. nov. Scale bar is 1.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/287339/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.287340>
    dc:description "FIGURES 11 – 14. Lateral photographs of heads and pronota. 11. U. assamensis; 12. U. jingae sp. nov.; 13. U. angusta sp. nov.; 14. U. magna sp. nov. Scale bar is 1.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/287340/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.287338>
    dc:description "FIGURES 5 – 6. Photographs of habitus. 5. U. angusta sp. nov.; 6. U. magna sp. nov. Scale bar is 1.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/287338/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.287341>
    dc:description "FIGURES 15 – 18. Ventral photographs of rostra and sulci. 15. U. assamensis; 16. U. jingae sp. nov.; 17. U. angusta sp. nov.; 18. U. magna sp. nov. Scale bar is 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/287341/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.287336>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 3. Photographs of habitus. 1. Ulonemia assamensis (Distant, 1903 a) (Guangxi); 2. U. assamensis (lectotype in the BMNH); 3. U. jingae sp. nov.. Scale bar is 1.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/287336/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.287342>
    dc:description "FIGURES 19 – 22. Ventral illustrations of female genitalia. 19. U. assamensis; 20. U. jingae sp. nov.; 21. U. angusta sp. nov.; 22. U. magna sp. nov. Scale bar is 1.0 mm. VII = seventh abdominal segment, Gcp-I = first gonocoxopodite, Pt-VIII = eighth paratergite, Pt-IX = ninth paratergite." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/287342/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

